===Reviews=== *[http://www.hardwarezone.com.ph/review-transcend-storejet-cloud-racing-cloud On '''HardWareZone'''] *[http://www.tweaktown.com/reviews/5482/transcend-storejet-cloud-32gb-wireless-storage-device-review/index.html On '''TweakTown'''] :Popping the rear cover off the StoreJet we found a 3.7v Lipo battery with a 2000mAh capacity. :Internally the StoreJet is rather impressive, housing a ''RTL8196C'' network processor, :along with 32GB of ''Toshiba'' MLC asynchronous NAND in a 2 x 16GB configuration. :At the bottom there is an ''Alcor Micro'' [http://www.alcormicro.com/en_content/c_product/product_02a.php?CategoryID=3 AU6998N] FSP.
